      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"impact\" feels so theoretical though. Like, if a tree falls in a forest and no one is around to hear it, it doesn't matter. I'm just drifting. I look at my life and it’s like there's no footprint left behind. It wouldn't be a tragedy, it would just be... quiet. Like nothing ever happened.",
